- Keep that (simple; recompute staff columns for all rows each run), or  
- Move this tab to **upsert-by-date** (only append/update new `date_local`s)?

### 11. Volume / Sheets limits
Rough order of magnitude: items per day? (e.g. 50 vs 500 lines/day changes whether full rebuild is fine.)

### 12. Primary use case
What decision does this tab support?

- Labor efficiency per item / category during rush  
- Staffing vs item throughput  
- Reconciling KDS times to labor  
- Something else  

That prioritizes which derived columns matter beyond headcount.

